edu.purdue.cs.barista

Class GradescopeListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.junit.runner.notification.RunListener
      • edu.purdue.cs.barista.GradescopeListener

  • public class GradescopeListener
extends org.junit.runner.notification.RunListener
    The GradescopeListener class is adapted from the GradedTestListener class from Tim Kutcher. Modifications have been made such that the TestCase annotation can be used in TestSuite classes.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    2.1.1, 06/21/2020
    Author:
    Andrew Davis, drew@drewdavis.me
